extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p We have created an employer account for #{firstName} on UK Visa Sponsorship.
  p We have already added some of your active visa sponsorship jobs to our platform to help you find candidates.
  p To access your account and manage your jobs, please click the button below to set your password and claim your account.
  p Please note: The jobs we added for you will remain active for 3 weeks from their posting date. After that, they will expire.
  p Also, this account invitation is valid for 3 weeks. If not claimed by then, the account will be deleted, and you will need to sign up manually using our registration form.
  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Claim My Account
